---
layout: default
title: AI Automations
description: Learn how artificial intelligence can automate repetitive tasks, streamline complex workflows, and significantly boost your productivity. Explore tools and techniques for AI-powered automation.
---
<main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">

    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">
        {{ title }}
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
        {{ description }}
    </p>

    {# Automations Grid #}
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {% for item in collections.automation %}
            <article class="article-card bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
                <a href="{{ item.url }}">
                    <img src="{{ item.data.teaser_image | url }}" alt="" class="w-full h-48 object-contain p-4 bg-gray-100">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold mb-2">Automation</span>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">
                            {{ item.data.title }}
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                            {{ item.data.summary }}
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                            {% set the_content = item.content %}
                            {% include "helpers/reading-time.njk" %}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </article>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>

</main>